description: Returns the ID and status of each active change set for a stack. For example, CloudFormation lists change sets that are in the CREATE_IN_PROGRESS or CREATE_PENDING state.

parameters.name: StackName
parameters.description: The name or the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the stack for which you want to list change sets.

nested_items.name: Summaries
nested_items.description: A list of ChangeSetSummary structures that provides the ID and status of each change set for the specified stack.

nested_items.name: StackId
nested_items.description: The ID of the stack with which the change set is associated.

nested_items.name: StackName
nested_items.description: The name of the stack with which the change set is associated.

nested_items.name: ChangeSetId
nested_items.description: The ID of the change set.

nested_items.name: ChangeSetName
nested_items.description: The name of the change set.

nested_items.name: ExecutionStatus
nested_items.description: If the change set execution status is AVAILABLE, you can execute the change set. If you can't execute the change set, the status indicates why. For example, a change set might be in an UNAVAILABLE state because CloudFormation is still creating it or in an OBSOLETE state because the stack was already updated.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The state of the change set, such as CREATE_PENDING, CREATE_COMPLETE, or FAILED.

nested_items.name: StatusReason
nested_items.description: A description of the change set's status. For example, if your change set is in the FAILED state, CloudFormation shows the error message.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The start time when the change set was created, in UTC.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: Descriptive information about the change set.

nested_items.name: IncludeNestedStacks
nested_items.description: Specifies the current setting of IncludeNestedStacks for the change set.

nested_items.name: ImportExistingResources
nested_items.description: Indicates if the change set imports resources that already exist.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If the output exceeds 1 MB, a string that identifies the next page of change sets. If there is no additional page, this value is null.
